meta.name: rabbitmq
meta.description: Dashboard for the telegraf input plug-in: RabbitMQ
meta.author: influxdata

queries.query: select mean("consumers") AS "consumers" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
select mean("exchanges") AS "exchanges" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
select mean("queues") AS "queues" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
select derivative(mean("messages_published"), 1s) AS "published_per_sec" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
select derivative(mean("messages_delivered"), 1s) AS "delivered_per_sec" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
select derivative(mean("messages_acked"), 1s) AS "acked_per_sec" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
select derivative(mean("messages_unacked"), 1s) AS "unacked_per_sec" from rabbitmq_overview WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host" = :host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
